Single-database configuration for Flask.
# flask_clinic
Flask Clinic Management System

A simple Flask application demonstrating a Doctor–Patient–Specialty–Appointment relational system using SQLAlchemy and Flask-Migrate.

This project is intended for learning, testing, or demo purposes.

Features

Models:

Specialty: Represents medical specialties (Cardiology, Neurology, etc.)

Doctor: Belongs to a specialty, can have multiple appointments

Patient: Can have multiple appointments

Appointment: Links a doctor and a patient with a scheduled date

Uses Flask SQLAlchemy for ORM

Database migrations handled via Flask-Migrate

Modular project structure (models.py, app.py)

Requirements

Python 3.8+

Flask

Flask-SQLAlchemy

Flask-Migrate